{"tid":2165003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Hello Goodbye 1997 電子書公開！！","createTime":"2020-08-19T13:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T07:21:59.000Z","uid":70063,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0c4809fa5d0fb46612f5e9c21aef410100f79bda","tid":2165003,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:53:18.000Z","msg":"Hello Goodbye 1997 電子書公開!!<br />\n<br />\n之前有讀者問本書重有冇得買? 首先好多謝各位厚愛, 不過本書舊年已經清咗倉喇。所以諗諗下不如以電子版形式公開, 但係由於電子版同當初印刷版一樣, 無奈亦都有相同嘅「編輯內容錯誤」(可在下邊第2條Link download), 講聲唔好意思先。<br />\n<br />\n另外, 對於各位讀者朋友欣賞拙作, 身為著者係好開心, 歡迎引用及轉載, 但係都同時希望能夠尊重知識產權, 引用嗰時加返credits, 多謝諒解同支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  。<br />\n<br />\nHello Goodbye 1997 電子書:<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1lYOhvnr606uoIvW6Tjirftldr5SitqNd/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1lYOhvnr606uoIvW6Tjirftldr5SitqNd%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufd8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=3a5360ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1lYOhvnr606uoIvW6Tjirftldr5SitqNd/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n編輯內容錯誤改正:<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1pJ_nwtR0WOYHJo0Cjp7CD2Yek3T6dU1R/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1pJ_nwtR0WOYHJo0Cjp7CD2Yek3T6dU1R%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufd8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=8a29b71a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1pJ_nwtR0WOYHJo0Cjp7CD2Yek3T6dU1R/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n#香港史<br />\n#電子書<br />\n#大英帝國<br />\n#香港文化<br />\n#殖民地<br />\n#九七<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p7Mh3MN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp7Mh3MN.jpg&h=110e203d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=686601795226510&amp;id=180641289155899\" data-sr-url=\"https://